>\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypySWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=7ef93b54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ec4ecb8570e5510e33f2f750d7d4543c8e2f5d7d","tid":1231584,"uid":236847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:43:10.000Z","msg":"啱啱放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚟緊"},{"pid":"ec3e02c035cdb044df56625d41c65b4616c36517","tid":1231584,"uid":44916,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"有啲一家大細，有老有嫩，係都安置晒佢哋先有後續"},{"pid":"ea9344d87e52a33612744a3a8a4359bacf1c13b9","tid":1231584,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:43:27.000Z","msg":"唔好畀林鄭睇死呀！香港人！"},{"pid":"debf9afe252c56369f8319b14a77b7e386d9deb8","tid":1231584,"uid":85057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:43:58.000Z","msg":"地鐵好多人等住走，"},{"pid":"e7cd30b3b9ab64b12e2d584109b83f58c9f32ac4","tid":1231584,"uid":261576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6684eddb86490bb9168ea5147125215414d7d63e","tid":1231584,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"點算？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:44:34.000Z","msg":"不撒回不撒退。已經有人用咪嗌人留停"},{"pid":"87367f3f043af3a47d456b905112b4b360d3c5f2","tid":1231584,"uid":22261